    AI-driven analysis of sensor data, vibration signals, and operational metrics to forecast equipment failures. 
    These solutions minimize unplanned downtime, extend asset lifespan, and reduce maintenance costs.
  </CompetenceCard>
  
  <CompetenceCard
    title="Robotics & Intelligent Control"
    subtitle="AI-driven automation and adaptive control systems"
    badge="SPECIALIZED"
