    Development of autonomous and semi-autonomous robotic systems with adaptive decision-making capabilities. 
    Our solutions improve throughput, reduce errors, and enable safe human-robot collaboration in industrial environments.
  </CompetenceCard>
  
  <CompetenceCard
    title="NLP & LLM Agent Systems"
