    Integration of natural language processing and large language model agents for process monitoring, 
    documentation automation, and intelligent decision support. These systems bridge human expertise 
    with AI-driven insights for faster, more accurate operations.
  </CompetenceCard>
  
  <CompetenceCard
    title="Computer Vision & Quality Control"
    subtitle="Automated inspection and defect detection"
    badge="SPECIALIZED"
    technologies={["Computer Vision", "CNN", "Image Processing", "Edge AI"]}
